{"tid":2388561,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"小鵬汽車創辦人何小鵬 : 中國企業太強讓Tesla 不安","createTime":"2021-01-31T08:37:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T14:45:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"81396dd6ed705c521b2834b4f301153c159b40ef","tid":2388561,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕中國電動車廠小鵬汽車（XPeng）近年來因自動駕駛方面的爭端，與特斯拉創辦人馬斯克（Elon Musk）多次隔空互懟。近日小鵬汽車聯合創辦人何小鵬在一場活動上談及爲何要與特斯拉創辦人馬斯克（Elon Musk）隔空互懟、針鋒相對，何小鵬稱，主要是因爲中國企業太強，讓特斯拉感到不安所致。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，何小鵬近日在出席創新大會2021活動上，談及早前為何與馬斯克隔空互懟，何小鵬稱「主要是因為中國企業效率更高創新更快，讓特斯拉感到不安，並不是只是因為小鵬一家。」<br />\n<br />\n何小鵬另也稱，儘管小鵬汽車在自動駕駛方面起步不算早，但有自信小鵬汽車在未來幾年可以做到世界第一，提供更安全的、全場景的無人駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n中媒指出，在中國國內造車新勢力陣營中，與特斯拉恩怨糾紛最多的車企，非小鵬汽車莫屬。據悉，此前小鵬汽車和特斯拉才因員工問題訴諸公堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3427737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3427737&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=b71c15bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3427737&h=a3bc7c4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3427737</a>"},{"pid":"b6df039fcefb5f5486b9e0c8bb5a8e93599100d0","tid":2388561,"uid":85127,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"人不笑 狗也吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b03eee32aa35f03844972e50cb8543dfdcd691c","tid":2388561,"uid":86673,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:39:53.000Z","msg":"小鴨電影都出名過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27654f96229dfa8efdab9d8093b9d8a3a2996eb9","tid":2388561,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"高價挖人"},{"pid":"bcf66ee2c6dc67ba0a26373c2a99549bc266d4bd","tid":2388561,"uid":68220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"係街冇見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國好賣得？"},{"pid":"6544d92411bf5e32dd58c0fc96e5ceae56b66a7d","tid":2388561,"uid":259901,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"乜tesla唔係中國企業咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e71319c81f1484514d65e472c9da4d875cc186","tid":2388561,"uid":244797,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"馬斯克tesla攢錢養space X<br />\n共產黨偷搶抄telsa<br />\n共產黨控制嘅美國民主黨ban space x<br />\n<br />\n最後space x失敗 tesla破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244cf696c30de7c84eeef8c536dbb2fe5f4870a6","tid":2388561,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢人？未聽過"},{"pid":"f5ccf9d9a0ba6558447b2b6d02d3dc51e9285b21","tid":2388561,"uid":241399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"中國企業（打飛機）太強"},{"pid":"2135d2872d8af2464358eaf44309aa7f4d07b79f","tid":2388561,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"爆起上黎真係太强 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6716f25b2ea68d21b20222828ccc0d1f479a75","tid":2388561,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"咁叻唔好抄人囉"},{"pid":"95459141c2e7968f46007459a7433aca727c6556","tid":2388561,"uid":355289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92e71319c81f1484514d65e472c9da4d875cc186","tid":2388561,"uid":244797,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"馬斯克tesla攢錢養space X<br />\n共產黨偷搶抄telsa<br />\n共產黨控制嘅美國民主黨ban space x<br />\n<br />\n最後spac